{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/customizing-coc-explorer/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Yeri's Blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"a701de20-db98-54e6-88a6-e83a640fdd64","excerpt":"Coc explorer is a coc.nvim extension that tries to mimic the file explorer feature of vscode. Here’s how it looks by default.  To make adjustment, we can open…","html":"<p><a href=\"https://github.com/weirongxu/coc-explorer\">Coc explorer</a> is a <a href=\"https://github.com/neoclide/coc.nvim/wiki/Using-coc-extensions\">coc.nvim</a> extension that tries to mimic the file explorer feature of vscode.</p>\n<p>Here’s how it looks by default.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/static/007393079ad8d94957db9ce606c00e13/b5a09/initial.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.75675675675676%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Initial looks\"\n        title=\"Initial looks\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/007393079ad8d94957db9ce606c00e13/fcda8/initial.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/007393079ad8d94957db9ce606c00e13/12f09/initial.png 148w,\n/blog/static/007393079ad8d94957db9ce606c00e13/e4a3f/initial.png 295w,\n/blog/static/007393079ad8d94957db9ce606c00e13/fcda8/initial.png 590w,\n/blog/static/007393079ad8d94957db9ce606c00e13/efc66/initial.png 885w,\n/blog/static/007393079ad8d94957db9ce606c00e13/c83ae/initial.png 1180w,\n/blog/static/007393079ad8d94957db9ce606c00e13/b5a09/initial.png 1360w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>To make adjustment, we can open coc config file using <code class=\"language-text\">:CocConfig</code> command and specify config option within <code class=\"language-text\">explorer</code> field.</p>\n<p>The first thing I want to change is the explorer width, I think its too wide.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\"><span class=\"token string\">\"explorer.width\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">30</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>The next thing is to tell it to display hidden files, because I work with a lot of dotfiles.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\"><span class=\"token string\">\"explorer.file.showHiddenFiles\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> true</code></pre></div>\n<p>When we open coc explorer, by default it will navigate to currently opened file in the tree.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/blog/22d4739e10f526126a828f411fb8cd53/coc-explorer-auto-reveal.gif\" alt=\"auto reveal by default\"></p>\n<p>I’m not really like the behaviour, so I disable it.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\"><span class=\"token string\">\"explorer.file.autoReveal\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> false</code></pre></div>\n<p>The popup window is also distracting rather than helpful, so I disable it also.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\"><span class=\"token string\">\"explorer.previewAction.onHover\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> false</code></pre></div>\n<p>I’d like to display some nice font icon, I’m using both nerdfont and devicons.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\"><span class=\"token string\">\"explorer.icon.enableVimDevicons\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> true\n<span class=\"token string\">\"explorer.icon.enableNerdfont\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> true</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/static/aacb541f7682e7626db345f972cbd05a/b5a09/with-icon.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.75675675675676%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"with icon\"\n        title=\"with icon\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/aacb541f7682e7626db345f972cbd05a/fcda8/with-icon.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/aacb541f7682e7626db345f972cbd05a/12f09/with-icon.png 148w,\n/blog/static/aacb541f7682e7626db345f972cbd05a/e4a3f/with-icon.png 295w,\n/blog/static/aacb541f7682e7626db345f972cbd05a/fcda8/with-icon.png 590w,\n/blog/static/aacb541f7682e7626db345f972cbd05a/efc66/with-icon.png 885w,\n/blog/static/aacb541f7682e7626db345f972cbd05a/c83ae/with-icon.png 1180w,\n/blog/static/aacb541f7682e7626db345f972cbd05a/b5a09/with-icon.png 1360w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>By default, coc explorer render ridiculous amount of whitespace after filename, of course I’m getting rid of that.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\"><span class=\"token string\">\"explorer.file.child.template\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"[git | 2] [selection | clip | 1] [indent][icon | 1] [diagnosticError &amp; 1][filename omitCenter 1][modified][readonly] [linkIcon &amp; 1][link growRight 1 omitCenter 5]\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Next, I tidy up the label a bit.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\"><span class=\"token string\">\"explorer.buffer.root.template\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"[icon &amp; 1] OPEN EDITORS\"</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">\"explorer.file.root.template\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"[icon &amp; 1] PROJECT ([root])\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>I also still use some mappings that I use in nerdtree.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\"><span class=\"token string\">\"explorer.keyMappings\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"s\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"open:vsplit\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"mm\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"rename\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"mc\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"copyFile\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"C\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"copyFile\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"md\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"delete\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"D\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"delete\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"ma\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"addFile\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"mA\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"addDirectory\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>Final result</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/static/cb082b086869b37a250fddd9e6d1588e/b5a09/final.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.75675675675676%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"final result\"\n        title=\"final result\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/cb082b086869b37a250fddd9e6d1588e/fcda8/final.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/cb082b086869b37a250fddd9e6d1588e/12f09/final.png 148w,\n/blog/static/cb082b086869b37a250fddd9e6d1588e/e4a3f/final.png 295w,\n/blog/static/cb082b086869b37a250fddd9e6d1588e/fcda8/final.png 590w,\n/blog/static/cb082b086869b37a250fddd9e6d1588e/efc66/final.png 885w,\n/blog/static/cb082b086869b37a250fddd9e6d1588e/c83ae/final.png 1180w,\n/blog/static/cb082b086869b37a250fddd9e6d1588e/b5a09/final.png 1360w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Full config:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\"><span class=\"token string\">\"explorer.width\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">30</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">\"explorer.buffer.root.template\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"[icon &amp; 1] OPEN EDITORS\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">\"explorer.file.root.template\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"[icon &amp; 1] PROJECT ([root])\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">\"explorer.file.child.template\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"[git | 2] [selection | clip | 1] [indent][icon | 1] [diagnosticError &amp; 1][filename omitCenter 1][modified][readonly] [linkIcon &amp; 1][link growRight 1 omitCenter 5]\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">\"explorer.file.showHiddenFiles\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> true<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">\"explorer.file.autoReveal\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> false<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">\"explorer.icon.enableVimDevicons\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> true<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">\"explorer.icon.enableNerdfont\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> true<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">\"explorer.previewAction.onHover\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> false<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token string\">\"explorer.keyMappings\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"s\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"open:vsplit\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"mm\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"rename\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"mc\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"copyFile\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"C\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"copyFile\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"md\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"delete\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"D\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"delete\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"ma\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"addFile\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"mA\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"addDirectory\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Customizing Coc Explorer","date":"September 23, 2020","description":"Here is how I customize coc-explorer, an alternative to nerdtree"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/customizing-coc-explorer/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/customizing-vim-lightline/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Customizing Vim Lightline"}},"next":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["1246554614","2841359383"]}